name: IllusionMix
description:
My new favorite model. Creates fantastic images with high amount of detail and beautiful colors.
- Already includes vae (kl-f8-anime2)

To get good quality pictures, I used highresfix with the following settings:
- Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x Anime 6B
- Steps: 5
- Denoising: 0.4
- Upscale by 2

Default style for example images:
- super resolution, super detailed, ultra detailed, masterpiece, best quality, {PasteHereYourPrompt}, (neutral colors), (hdr:1.3)
- (worst quality, low quality:1.4), text, watermark, (monochrome), frame, (deformed, distorted, disfigured:1.3), poorly drawn, bad anatomy, wrong anatomy, extra limb, missing limb, floating limbs, (mutated hands and fingers:1.4), disconnected limbs, mutation, mutated, ugly, disgusting, blurry, amputation, {PasteHereYourPrompt}
